OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773245484
OL,3,CHistorical figures on banknotes to be
OL,4,Creplaced with British wildlife
OL,6,FHistorical figures on banknotes are
OL,7,Fset to be replaced by images of the
OL,8,FUK's wildlife, with the public allowed
OL,9,Fto choose what should be featured.
OL,11,FFor more than 50 years, notable people
OL,12,Ffrom Britain's history have been
OL,13,Fshowcased on the notes, such as Sir
OL,14,FWinston Churchill, Alan Turing, and
OL,15,FJane Austen.
OL,17,FBut the Bank of England said this week
OL,18,Fthat the change to wildlife creates an
OL,19,Fopportunity to celebrate different
OL,20,Faspects of the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
