OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773245484
OL,3,CHistorical figures on banknotes to be
OL,4,Creplaced with British wildlife
OL,6,FIt also makes it more difficult for
OL,7,Fthe notes to be counterfeited while
OL,8,Fmaking security features more
OL,9,Fdistinguishable, the central bank said.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
