OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773245484
OL,3,CHistorical figures on banknotes to be
OL,4,Creplaced with British wildlife
OL,6,FThe decision comes after a
OL,7,Fconsultation over what theme should
OL,8,Ffeature on the notes. Wildlife came
OL,9,Ftop with a vote share of 60%, followed
OL,10,Fby architecture and landmarks (56%),
OL,11,Fnotable historical figures (38%),
OL,12,Farts, culture, and sports (30%),
OL,13,Finnovation (23%), and noteworthy
OL,14,Fmilestones (19%).
OL,16,FIt was based on 44,000 responses from
OL,17,Fonline surveys, emails, and designs
OL,18,Fsubmitted by schools and the general
OL,19,Fpublic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773245484
OL,3,CHistorical figures on banknotes to be
OL,4,Creplaced with British wildlife
OL,6,FA second consultation will run this
OL,7,Fsummer to gather views on the specific
OL,8,Fwildlife that should feature, which
OL,9,Fcan include plants, landscapes, and
OL,10,Fanimals.
OL,12,FIt will be several years before the
OL,13,Fbanknotes are issued, and they will
OL,14,Fcontinue to show a portrait of the
OL,15,Fmonarch.
OL,17,FRepresentation of the Home Nations `
OL,18,FEngland, Scotland, Wales, and Northern
OL,19,FIreland ` will be an important factor
OL,20,Fof the design.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
