PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773245484
OL,3,CHistorical figures on banknotes to be
OL,4,Creplaced with British wildlife
OL,6,FVictoria Cleland, chief cashier at the
OL,7,FBank of England, said nature is a
OL,8,Fgreat choice "from a banknote
OL,9,Fauthentication perspective" and "means
OL,10,Fwe can showcase the UK's rich and
OL,11,Fvaried wildlife on the next series of
OL,12,Fbanknotes".
OL,14,F"I look forward to hearing about the
OL,15,Fpublic's favourite wildlife during our
OL,16,Fforthcoming summer consultation."
OL,18,FThe Conservative Party was less
OL,19,Fenthusiastic in its response to the
OL,20,Fnew theme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
