PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773245484
OL,3,CHistorical figures on banknotes to be
OL,4,Creplaced with British wildlife
OL,6,FAlex Burghart MP, Shadow Chancellor of
OL,7,Fthe Duchy of Lancaster, said: "It is
OL,8,Fdeeply depressing that under Labour
OL,9,Four national heroes are considered too
OL,10,F'divisive' to be on the banknotes.
OL,11,FMost countries celebrate their history
OL,12,F- ours should too."
OL,14,F"Only the Conservatives, under new
OL,15,Fleadership, will restore pride in our
OL,16,Fhistory and common-sense governance."
OL,18,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,19,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,20,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,21,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
